; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/linux/zathura.md

% zathura, linux

# Open a file
zathura <path_to_file>

# Navigate left/up/down/right
<_h___j___k___l___ArrowKeys_>

# Rotate
<r>

# Invert Colors
<Ctrl r>

# Search for text by a given string
</><string>

# Create/delete bookmarks
<:><bmark_bdelete> <bookmark_name><Enter>

# List bookmarks
<:>blist<Enter>

# Follow links
<f><link_number><Enter>
